description: Sparx Holdings Group, Inc. does not have significant operations. It focuses on effecting a merger, capital stock exchange, asset acquisition, stock purchase, reorganization, or related business combination with one or more businesses. The company intends to explore business opportunities in the area of fire suppression technologies. Sparx Holdings Group, Inc. was formerly known as Prime Time Holdings, Inc. and changed its name to Sparx Holdings Group, Inc. in July 2022. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is headquartered in Cranston, Rhode Island.
